MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2001-Cab
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 22nd July, 2001
31 Asadha, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to say that Shri Ajit Singh has been sworn in
as Cabinet Minister by the President at 1800 hours, today, the 22nd July, 2001
in the Rashtrapati Bhavan, New Delhi.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary

To

(P. Gopalakrishnan)
